Package othellogame.ui.view

Class GameInstructionsView

java.lang.Object
othellogame.ui.view.GameInstructionsView
public class GameInstructionsView extends Object
Represents the controller for the GameInstructionsScene FXML file in the Othello game application.

It manages the UI elements and actions associated with the GameInstructionsScene FXML file.

Follows the Model-View-Controller (MVC) pattern.

Version:
1.0, 12/07/2023
Author:
Dinh Thuy Nhat Vy
